Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.36,0:28:37.97,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}呐 我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.20,0:28:43.63,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}愛是什麼
